Package: bscui
Type: Package
Title: Build SVG Custom User Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Patrice", "Godard",
        role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
        email = "patrice.godard@gmail.com"
    )
    )
Description: Render SVG as interactive figures with selectable and clickable
   user interface elements. These figures can be integrated in markdown
   documents or in shiny applications reacting to events triggered on them.
   Features also include moving, zoom in/out and export in SVG or PNG formats.
URL:
   https://patzaw.github.io/bscui/,
   https://github.com/patzaw/bscui/
BugReports: https://github.com/patzaw/bscui/issues
Depends:
   R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
   htmlwidgets
Suggests:
   knitr,
   rmarkdown,
   here,
   xml2,
   dplyr,
   readr,
   stringr,
   glue,
   shiny,
   DT,
   colourpicker
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
